```

Repeat for every file. Paths must be relative (e.g. src/main.py, package.json). Use a language tag on the fence (python, javascript, etc.).

Legacy alternate (still supported): put the relative path alone on one line, then a fenced block on the next lines:

relative/path/to/file.ext
```
